}

  width: 100%;

  display: inline-block;
  width: 100%;

  padding-left: 22px;

}
.radio span::before, .radio span::after {
  margin-top: 1px;
}
.radio span::before {
  box-sizing: content-box;
  content: "";
  display: inline-block;
  position: absolute;
  width: 10px;
  height: 10px;
  top: 1px;
  left: 1px;
  margin-left: 0;
  border: 2px solid #000000;
  border-radius: 100%;
  transition: border-color 0.1s ease-in-out;
  -webkit-transition: border-color 0.1s ease-in-out;
  background-color: transparent;
}
.radio span::after {
  box-sizing: content-box;
  position: absolute;
  content: "";
  width: 6px;
  height: 6px;

  margin-left: 0;

  border-radius: 100%;
  opacity: 0;
}

  color: #000000;
}

  z-index: 3;

.personal-settings-modal.modal .modal-dialog.modal-xlg {
  width: 900px;
  height: 600px;
}

.tab-content > .active {
  margin-left: 10px;
}

iframe {
  border-right: none;
  border-left: none;
  border-top: none;
  border-bottom: none;
}

#userSettingsPage .opr-form-item-controls > *, #userPasswordPage .opr-form-item-controls > * {
  width: 320px;
}

#userSettingsPage .opr-form-item-label, #userPasswordPage .opr-form-item-label {
  width: 150px;
}

#userSettingsPage .reset-user-settings {
  margin-top: 15px;
}

#userSettingsPage .reset-user-settings .btn {
  margin-top: 10px;
}

#userSettingsPage .reset-user-settings .description {
  margin-top: 10px;
  margin-left: 50px;
}

#userSettingsPage .reset-user-settings .opr-icon.icon-dialog-warning {
  position: absolute;
  left: 20px;
}

.user-settings-checkbox {
  text-align: left;
}

.navbar-body {
  padding-bottom: 10px;
}

.personal-settings-modal.modal {
  top: 15%;
}

.personal-settings-modal.modal .modal-dialog.modal-xlg .modal-content .modal-body {
  max-height: 470px;
}

#recipient {
	overflow: hidden;
}

@media screen and (min-width: 992px) {
  .personal-settings-modal.modal .modal-dialog.modal-custom {
    width: 900px;
  }
}

@media screen and (max-width: 992px) {
  .personal-settings-modal.modal .modal-dialog.modal-custom {
    width: 600px;
  }
}

@media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
  .personal-settings-modal.modal .modal-dialog.modal-custom {
    width: 420px;
  }
}
